title: Four area high school football teams land spots in the Plays of the Week
text:
Four area high school football teams land spots in the Plays of the Week 
Updated: Sun, Oct 25 2015, 11:34 PM 
Stream WZTV Fox 17 Newscasts LIVE starting with Fox 17 This Morning at 4:30am, News at 5:30pm and News at 9pm & 10 pm 

Here's a snipit of the Plays of the Week with FOX 17's Paul Jones and Dave Foster. The football teams from Riverdale, Shelbyville Central, Camden Central, and Davidson Academy landing spots in the Top 10.
